    {
      "id": "54e17234-1395-42fd-9420-6d527e19dc3a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose the introduction of temporal data in models meant to predict student performance. Authors show that within- and between-semester features could be utilized to predict success.",
