      "id": "96d6e169-34aa-4c37-abe1-3bddc8282603",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors show effectiveness of approach by using a sample of 10 years of data collected from UNC Charlotte for between-semester interactions. Within-semester activities were measured using an introductory course in Computer Science. ",
